txt.en: Fighting in the Ettenmoors and completing the requests here will earn you greater rewards. There are a series of important objectives found throughout the Ettenmoors that must be undertaken.
Complete the Weekly: Ettenmoors Major quest
Complete the quest Weekly: Ettenmoors Moderate
Complete the Weekly: Ettenmoors Minor quest
Complete a support quest in the Ettenmoors ([placeholder]/20)
Complete a kill enemy quest in the Ettenmoors ([placeholder]/10)
Battling in the Ettenmoors greatly rewards those who are consistent participants. Complete this quest to earn your share of the rewards.
Advancement toward the weekly war effort ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

'As the battle persists, we have discovered that there are wares within our coffers that we can share with all who fight in the Free Peoples' interest. Undertake the tasks presented and you will earn your share of these spoils.\n\n'We must remain vigilant against the darkness spreading in these lands.'
Weekly: Battle Across the Ettenmoors - Tier 1
Complete requests to earn rewards from the war effort
